        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7945",
        "content": "The two guests were an Englishman and his wife, whom the chances of travel had brought over night to Valedolmo.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
