        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7945",
        "content": "The man is scarcely to blame for his name.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7945_112011_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7945/112011/7945_112011_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7945",
        "content": "'I suppose not,' she agreed, 'though I should have included that in my order.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7945_112011_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7945/112011/7945_112011_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7945",
        "content": "Further discussion was precluded by the appearance of a station carriage which turned in at the gate and stopped before them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7945_112011_000047_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7945/112011/7945_112011_000047_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7945",
        "content": "He had not counted upon this addition to the party, and was as scowling as she could have wished.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
